{\line }

{\line }
\uc1\u8220"Hush milady, we know not. But no body to be found, or a trace of cloth, we can be sure. Have hope, Lady Celia. And let not a soul know of this.\uc1\u8221"
{\line }

{\line }
The man left a hint of consolation in his voice but none of that would be enough for Celia now.
{\line }

{\line }
