Lanris paused momentarily and furrowed his brow before continuing to eat slowly, more so because he wasn\uc1\u8217't too fond of Mott\uc1\u8217's stew rather than because he was savoring it. Mott on the other hand was scraping the last spoonfuls from his canteen, and was quite possibly going to refill it soon. Dekar Pirru went on:
{\line }

{\line }
\uc1\u8220"I see that didn\uc1\u8217't get your attention, did it? Nothing short of your discharge papers would, I guess. The thing is, seems he had a talk with the General. Didn\uc1\u8217't last long. Short and to the point, his staff officers seem to say.\uc1\u8221"
