{\line }
Lanris threw a sideways glance at Mott, before throwing a piece of bread-pie to his head as well. He did not add a verbal insult though, and kept trying to consume the broth left in his canteen. Pirru grinned at Mott\uc1\u8217's comment and said with a slight edge of worry in his voice:
