{\line }
\uc1\u8220"No, I\uc1\u8217'm afraid his Holiness has not expressed any sort of death wish. I\uc1\u8217'm sure you\uc1\u8217'd be happy to serve in that case. In the most literal sense. Word around the staff officers is there has been a change of plans.\uc1\u8221"
