{\line }
\uc1\u8220"Dekar, how come you got by all these news? It\uc1\u8217's not like you to run around staff officers like Himmdal and Rynse do. You\uc1\u8217've said it yourself; if we even get a whiff about you sucking up to a staff officer, we can strip that dekar badge ourselves. So shall we each grab an arm and do the deed?\uc1\u8221"
{\line }

{\line }
Dekar Pirru looked at Lanris with one eye pointing a finger at him, his rasp voice making the threat almost believable:
{\line }

{\line }
\uc1\u8220"Wise-guys get picket duty on the northern face. I\uc1\u8217'll make sure we stick you on the fence itself. You\uc1\u8217'll make a good scarecrow.\uc1\u8221"
