{\line }
\uc1\u8220"Yeah, he went to the \uc1\u8217'Cent. Probably ripped him off too. Like the last time when he asked ten coin for some real Iolathan wine that turned out to be vinegar. Not even winegar, mind you. Plain old vinegar from the pharmacium stores. He even had the nerve to insist that it was a vintage bottle that had could be easily mistaken for vinegar by someone who wasn\uc1\u8217't a connoisseur. I think he meant you, dekar.\uc1\u8221"
