{\line }
\uc1\u8220"You should\uc1\u8217've pushed for rank, Lanris. Field Maggot Lanris has a ring to it, doesn\uc1\u8217't it? Anyway, spare me the dung talk. I got some details on that meeting as well. \uc1\u8217'Cent says that we\uc1\u8217're waiting for some new marching orders.\uc1\u8221"
{\line }

{\line }
\uc1\u8220"Not the Widelands then?\uc1\u8221", Mott cut in with enthusiasm, a glimmer of hope in his words.
