{\line }
Pirru sighed, before uttering a mild curse concerning Mott\uc1\u8217's mother. He went on, concentrating his focus on Lanris who was now listening more intently, having sat up and facing the dekar. He offered his pipe to Pirru who refused it with a slight nod, and went on:
{\line }

{\line }
\uc1\u8220"Mott, just shut up and go to sleep. As I was saying, there\uc1\u8217's a lot going on. I just hope the General knows his stuff so we don\uc1\u8217't end up on the wrong side of the turf.\uc1\u8221"
